snippet.title: OZYMANDIAS - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1768280?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=announcement

Build an empire in a single sitting in Ozymandias, a fast-paced 4X strategy game where economy is the deciding factor. Each turn, choose to expand your territory, grow your cities or attack your neighbours.
